data.description: Impeccable and well maintained home conveniently located in popular Tealwood Oaks Subdivision. All three public schools, Garden Ridge Elementary, Shadow Ridge Middle and Flower Mound High School have earned A ratings based on 2022 rankings. This beautiful home features four bedrooms and two full baths, two living areas and two dining rooms. One of the bedrooms can easily serve as a study. The kitchen opens to a large family room which offers a gas fireplace. Included is Granite counter tops, Stainless Steel appliances, upgraded lighting and much more. The roof was replaced in 2023 with upgraded venting along with fresh paint and new carpet. Relax in your large back yard while enjoying your expansive patio and heated salt water pool and spa.
